<TR bgcolor="99cc99"><TD>
	Product Description
</TD><TD>
	The AT970 "StreamView" by Sencore is designed to provide real time ATSC monitoring in a transmission environment. The AT970 acheives this by continuously monitoring up to four ATSC transport streams in real-time, verifying they conform to ATSC specifications. The "StreamView" performs all measurements in real-time and displays table information from each transport stream. Transport stream error status is provided at a glance with in-depth error reporting available through the Graphical User Interface. For those requiring a fully integrated monitoring tool, the AT970 is the solution by providing a fully remote controllable and monitoring via Ethernet through either Windows NT or Simple Network Management Protocol (SNMP). 
</TD></TR>		



																 																		
